# =============================================================================
# Nexus Environment Configuration
# =============================================================================
# 
# IMPORTANT: All features work WITHOUT an API key. The key only enables
# enhanced natural language understanding in the AI chat.
#
# To get started quickly:
#   1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env
#   2. Start the server: ./deploy.sh
#   3. Open http://localhost:5173
#
# To add enhanced AI features later:
#   1. Get an API key from https://console.anthropic.com/
#   2. Uncomment and fill in below
#   3. Restart the server
# =============================================================================

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTIONAL: Anthropic API Key for Enhanced AI Chat
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Without this key: AI chat uses rule-based analysis (fast, accurate, free)
# With this key: AI chat uses Claude LLM for more natural conversation
# 
# Cost: ~$0.01-0.05 per conversation
# Get your key: https://console.anthropic.com/
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# MODEL_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-your-key-here

# Alternative variable name (either works):
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-your-key-here

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTIONAL: Workspace Directory
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Where campaign data and logs are stored
# NEXUS_WORKSPACE=./workspace

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# OPTIONAL: Server Ports
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Change if ports are already in use on your system
# BACKEND_PORT=8000
# FRONTEND_PORT=5173
